2m (enables trace messages for operations on the ref database)                                  \r\n\u001b[4C\u001b[0;m\u001b[KTRACE_SHALLOW\u001b[0;2m (enables trace messages that can help debugging fetching/cloning of shallow re...)        \u001b[0;m\r\n\u001b[J\u001b[A\u001b[16A\r\u001b[24C\u001b[?25h"]
